item.description: l— title: “Wait Times at Walt Disney World” author: ‘Mikayla’ date: ‘2019-04-22’ slug: wait-times-at-walt-disney-world tags: [] categories: [] — The data used for this analysis was originally published by Touring Plans. I used the data for six rides: two from the Magic Kingdom (Seven Dwarfs Mine Train & Splash Mountain), two from Hollywood Studios (Toy Story Mania & The Rockin Rollercoaster), and two from Epcot (Soarin & Spaceship Earth).
